auth.welcomeText:
Hi {{firstName}},

Welcome to Nasta! Please verify your email to get started.

Verify your email: {{verificationLink}}

Or use this code in the app: {{token}}

If you didn’t create an account, you can ignore this email.

auth.verifyEmailText:
Please verify your email address.

Verification link: {{verificationLink}}

Or use this code in the app: {{token}}

If you didn’t request this, you can ignore this email.

admin.welcomeText:
Hi {{firstName}} {{lastName}},

An admin account has been created for you.

Email: {{email}}
Temporary password: {{password}}
Capabilities: {{capabilities}}

Please sign in and change your password immediately.

Best regards,
Nasta Team

support.ticketCreatedText:
Hi {{userName}},

Thanks for contacting Nasta support. We’ve created your ticket.

Ticket number: {{ticketNumber}}
Subject: {{subject}}
Category: {{category}}
Priority: {{priority}}

Our team will review your request and reply as soon as possible.

Best regards,
Nasta Support Team

support.abuseReportText:
Hi {{userName}},

Thank you for reporting abuse. We have received your report and created a ticket.

Ticket number: {{ticketNumber}}
Subject: {{subject}}
Priority: {{priority}}

Our safety team will review this report and take appropriate action if needed.

If you or someone else is in immediate danger, contact local emergency services.

Best regards,
Nasta Safety Team

support.securityReportText:
Hi {{userName}},

Thank you for reporting a security concern. We’ve created a ticket for your report.

Ticket number: {{ticketNumber}}
Subject: {{subject}}
Priority: {{priority}}

Our security team will investigate and may reach out for more details.

Best regards,
Nasta Security Team

